snippet.title: Kitchen Wars Game trailer.
snippet.description:
Kitchen Wars is a fast-paced multiplayer game that combines kitchen management with chaotic brawler action! Compete in head-to-head battles between two rival restaurants 🏨🍔 as you cook, serve, and sabotage your opponents in hilarious and creative ways. Balance strategy, combat ⚔️, and teamwork to outwit your rivals and claim culinary victory! 🥇🔥

🎮Wishlist Kitchen Wars On Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2955840/Kitchen_Wars/

🎮Demo available on Itch.io:
https://perfectgen.itch.io/kw

🎮Follow Kitchen Wars on Game Jolt:
https://gamejolt.com/games/KitchenWars/955401
